http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/karnataka/Farmer-dies-in-accident/article13993252.ece

A 55-year-old farmer died, while his friend was injured, when a Karnataka State Road Transport Corporation (KSRTC) bus collided with their motorcycle near Halaguru in Malavalli taluk in the district on Sunday.The Halaguru police have identified the deceased as K. Mahadevu, the rider, and the injured as Mayappa, both residents of Banasamudra.They were travelling towards Malavalli while the bus was coming from the opposite direction, said the police.Mayappa was rushed to a hospital. The police impounded the bus. Further investigation is on.